t|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Arai Hakuseki|ja|新井白石|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a Rōjū and Confucian scholar (born [[1657]]). (Note: Some sources record May 10 for this event.) * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1862]] {{ill|June 16|ja|6月16日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Shūnoyama Raigorō|ja|秀ノ山雷五郎|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 9th Yokozuna (born [[1808]]).
