{{Lunisolar May}} '''May 19''' is the 19th day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Enryaku|ja|延暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 21st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[802]] {{ill|June 22|ja|6月22日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Following a major eruption of {{ill|Mount Fuji|ja|富士山|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, which caused a collapse of the old Ashikaga Road, a new route called the Hakone Road was opened.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://example.org|title=Historical Eruption of Mt. Fuji and the Hakone Road|date=2021-03}}</ref> * [[:en:Eiroku|Eiroku]] 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1560]] {{ill|June 12|ja|6月12日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – At the Battle of Okehazama, {{ill|Oda Nobunaga|ja|織田信長|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} ambushed and defeated {{ill|Imagawa Yoshimoto|ja|今川義元|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} while he was resting in a field near the mountain. * [[:en:Eiroku|Eiroku]] 8th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1565]] {{ill|June 17|ja|6月17日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – In Kyoto, the 13th shōgun of the Ashikaga Shogunate, {{ill|Ashikaga Yoritoki|ja|足利義輝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, was attacked and killed. * {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 16th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1639]] {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Bunroku Monpu|ja|沢庵宗彭|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} entered the Buddhist priesthood at Tōkai-ji in Shinagawa, Edo. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1868]] {{ill|July 8|ja|7月8日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The Meiji government issued its first official government banknotes, known as the {{ill|Taiseikan-satsu|ja|太政官札|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Births == * {{ill|Man'en|ja|万延|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1860]] {{ill|July 7|ja|7月7日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Miyake Setsurō|ja|三宅雪嶺|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, an intellectual (died [[1945]]).
