ll|June 13|ja|6月13日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Miyamoto Musashi|ja|宮本武蔵|qq=}}, a renowned swordsman (born [[1584]]). * {{ill|Tenna|ja|天名|qq=}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1681]] {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Sakai Tadashige|ja|酒井忠清|qq=}}, a Tairō of the Tokugawa shogunate (born [[1624]]). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1725]] {{ill|June 29|ja|6月29日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Arai Hakuseki|ja|新井白石|qq=}}, a Rōjū and Confucian scholar (born [[1657]]). (Note: Some sources record May 10 for this event.) * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|qq=}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=}} [[1862]] {{ill|June 16|ja|6月16日|qq=}}) – {{ill|Shūnoyama Raigorō|ja|秀ノ山雷五郎|qq=}}, the 9th Yokozuna (born [[1808]]).
