|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1645]] {{ill|June 13|ja|6月13日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Miyamoto Musashi|ja|宮本武蔵|qq=|12=draft}}, a renowned swordsman (born [[1584]]). * {{ill|Tenna|ja|天名|qq=|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1681]] {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Sakai Tadashige|ja|酒井忠清|qq=|12=draft}}, a Tairō of the Tokugawa shogunate (born [[1624]]). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=|12=draft}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1725]] {{ill|June 29|ja|6月29日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Arai Hakuseki|ja|新井白石|qq=|12=draft}}, a Rōjū and Confucian scholar (born [[1657]]). (Note: Some sources record May 10 for this event.) * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|qq=|12=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1862]] {{ill|June 16|ja|6月16日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Shūnoyama Raigorō|ja|秀ノ山雷五郎|qq=|12=draft}}, the 9th Yokozuna (born [[1808]]).
