лендарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1639]] {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Bunroku Monpu|ja|沢庵宗彭|qq=|qq=draft}} entered the Buddhist priesthood at Tōkai-ji in Shinagawa, Edo. * {{ill|Meiji|ja|明治|1=Meiji era|qq=|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1868]] {{ill|July 8|ja|7月8日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – The Meiji government issued its first official government banknotes, known as the {{ill|Taiseikan-satsu|ja|太政官札|qq=|qq=draft}}.
== Births == * {{ill|Man'en|ja|万延|qq=|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1860]] {{ill|July 7|ja|7月7日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Miyake Setsurō|ja|三宅雪嶺|qq=|qq=draft}}, an intellectual (died [[1945]]).
== Deaths == * {{ill|Shitoku (Japan)|ja|至徳|qq=|qq=draft}} 1st year / {{ill|Genchū|ja|元中|qq=|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1384]] {{ill|June 8|ja|6月8日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Kan'ami|ja|観阿弥|qq=|qq=draft}}, an actor of Noh (born [[1333]]). * {{ill|Eiroku|ja|永禄|qq=|qq=draft}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1560]] {{ill|June 12|ja|6月12日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Imagawa Yoshimoto|ja|今川義元|qq=|qq=draft}}, a military commander (born [[1519]]). * {{ill|Eiroku|ja|永禄|qq=|qq=draft}} 8th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1565]] {{ill|June 17|ja|6月17日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Ashikaga Yoritoki|ja|足利義輝|qq=|qq=draft}}, the 13th shōgun of the Ashikaga Shogunate (born [[1536]]). * {{ill|Keichō|ja|慶長|qq=|qq=draft}} 4th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1599]] {{ill|July 11|ja|7月11日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Chōsōga–be Motonaga|ja|長宗我部元親|qq=|qq=draft}}, a military commander (born [[1539]]). * {{ill|Shōhō|ja|正保|qq=|qq=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1645]] {{ill|June 13|ja|6月13日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Miyamoto Musashi|ja|宮本武蔵|qq=|qq=draft}}, a renowned swordsman (born [[1584]]). * {{ill|Tenna|ja|天名|qq=|qq=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1681]] {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Sakai Tadashige|ja|酒井忠清|qq=|qq=draft}}, a Tairō of the Tokugawa shogunate (born [[1624]]). * {{ill|Kyōhō|ja|享保|qq=|qq=draft}} 10th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1725]] {{ill|June 29|ja|6月29日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Arai Hakuseki|ja|新井白石|qq=|qq=draft}}, a Rōjū and Confucian scholar (born [[1657]]). (Note: Some sources record May 10 for this event.) * {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|qq=|qq=draft}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|qq=draft}} [[1862]] {{ill|June 16|ja|6月16日|qq=|qq=draft}}) – {{ill|Shūnoyama Raigorō|ja|秀ノ山雷五郎|qq=|qq=draft}}, the 9th Yokozuna (born [[1808]]).
