== Deaths == * {{ill|Shitoku (Japan)|ja|至徳|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Shitoku (Japan)|qq=|comment=enwiki is a redirect}} 1st year / [[:en:Genchū|Genchū]] 1st year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1384|1384]] [[:en:June 8|June 8]]) – [[:en:Kan'ami|Kan'ami]], an actor of Noh (born [[:en:1333|1333]]). * [[:en:Eiroku|Eiroku]] 3rd year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1560|1560]] [[:en:June 12|June 12]]) – [[:en:Imagawa Yoshimoto|Imagawa Yoshimoto]], a military commander (born [[:en:1519|1519]]). * [[:en:Eiroku|Eiroku]] 8th year ([[:en:Julian calendar|Julian calendar]] [[:en:1565|1565]] [[:en:June 17|June 17]]) – [[:en:Ashikaga Yoshiteru|Ashikaga Yoritoki]], the 13th shōgun of the Ashikaga Shogunate (born [[:en:1536|1536]]). * [[:en:Keichō|Keichō]] 4th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1599]] [[:en:July 11|July 11]]) – [[:en:Chōsokabe Motochika|Chōsōga–be Motonaga]], a military commander (born [[:en:1539|1539]]). * [[:en:Shōhō|Shōhō]] 2nd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1645]] [[:en:June 13|June 13]]) – [[:en:Miyamoto Musashi|Miyamoto Musashi]], a renowned swordsman (born [[:en:1584|1584]]). * {{ill|Tenna|ja|天名|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenna|qq=|ja_comment=jawiki link invalid}} 1st year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1681]] [[:en:July 4|July 4]]) – [[:en:Sakai Tadakiyo|Sakai Tadashige]], a Tairō of the Tokugawa shogunate (born [[1624]]). * [[:en:Kyōhō|Kyōhō]] 10th year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1725]] [[:en:June 29|June 29]]) – [[:en:Arai Hakuseki|Arai Hakuseki]], a Rōjū and Confucian scholar (born [[1657]]). (Note: Some sources record May 10 for this event.) * [[:en:Bunkyū|Bunkyū]] 2nd year ([[:en:Gregorian calendar|Gregorian calendar]] [[1862]] [[:en:June 16|June 16]]) – [[:en:Hidenoyama Raigorō|Shūnoyama Raigorō]], the 9th Yokozuna (born [[1808]]).
